title: Lamb chops with herb spiced butter
ingredients: ['100g butter, softened', '1 tablespoon garlic, crushed', '60g onion, finely chopped', '25g breadcrumbs', '1 teaspoon ground cumin', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', 'A pinch of cayenne pepper', '30g fresh parsley, finely chopped', '30g fresh coriander, finely chopped', '4 lamb chops']
